> **IMPORTANT:** All icons for all levels need to be filled in as finished for this module to be considered 100% complete. An icon will not be changed to green or grey unless you click a continue or a submit button. As you progress through the levels, check back periodically to ensure the levels you have completed are recorded as being successfully finished.

<h4><details>
<summary>click here to see more about levels</summary>
<br>

<div><em>once you're finished viewing this, click the arrow above to collapse the section</em></div>
<br>
<img src ="/script_assets/pd/pd_level_overview.gif" />
</details></h4>

<br>

__Accessing levels__ can be done four ways:
<ol><li>clicking from the main page, </li><li> clicking to a different level in the same stage with the circles on the header of the page,</li><li> advance to the next level by clicking "continue" or "submit" at the bottom of each level (<bold>NOTE: this is the way you'll advance through most activities in Code Studio</bold>) </li>
<li>using the drop-down menu in the header can be used to access any level (this is helpful for going back to a level you've completed before)</li></ol>

